<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6b3d8d7c-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s535i"><num value="535i">§ 535i.</num><heading> Reservation of right to alter or repeal</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The right to alter, amend, or repeal this subchapter is expressly reserved.</p>
